        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Protecting and Preserving Social Security Act</strong></p> <p>This bill revises methods for calculating various aspects of Social Security benefits, eliminates the cap on compensation subject to Social Security taxes, and extends eligibility for Social Security benefits during the month of a beneficiary's death.</p>   ]]></text>
      </summary>
